ðŸš€ Deployment on GitHub Pages
- Create a GitHub repo named portfolio-website.
- Push your files (index.html, style.css, images/) to the repo.
- Go to Settings > Pages.
- Under Source, select main branch and /root.
- Click Save â€” your site will be live at https://yourusername.github.io/portfolio-website.

Want help customizing the design, adding animations, or integrating a contact form? I can help you level it up!
